was enough, wasn't it♪

10
00:00:41,236 --> 00:00:42,356
=Taking Love as a Contract=

11
00:00:42,868 --> 00:00:46,516
=Episode 9=
(I can make time)

12
00:00:49,600 --> 00:00:52,320
We're proposing

13
00:00:52,320 --> 00:00:54,400
